name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
Today, some netizens discovered that the deputy secretary of the Party Committee of Qinghai Nationalities University was proposed to be admitted as a doctoral student with the first place in the written test. Regarding netizens' questions about whether this was suspected of "being an athlete and a referee" and whether he was over the age limit, the staff said that the relevant person met the application requirements and "he was just a candidate." 
On April 13, Qinghai Nationalities University issued an announcement that its proposed doctoral admission qualification was cancelled
